<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从前，森林里住着一只蚱蜢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喜欢躺在草丛里唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啦啦啦！啊！多么美好的一天啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天天气很好，几只蚂蚁列队走过蚱蜢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚂蚁在附近停下来休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！你们几个！在干吗呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在收集食物。天真热啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们蚂蚁真愚蠢！今天太热了，不适合工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过来和我一起享受凉爽的草丛吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们得为冬天做准备。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天？还得过好几个月才到冬天呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们有大把的时间放松和玩乐！改天再为冬天做准备吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们现在就得准备。冬天会比你想象的来得快。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我们没有太多时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们太愚蠢了！冬天来了再准备吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚂蚁们扛着食物离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚱蜢一点儿也不担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他已经收集了足够一整天吃的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有足够的食物坚持到今天晚上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么要担心明天呢？我可以以后再摘些叶子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天，蚱蜢都唱着歌，在凉爽的草丛里休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>秋天来了。蚂蚁们比以前更忙了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂，你们几个！为什么不过来和我一起玩儿呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有时间玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么会没有时间呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天很快就要来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“愚蠢的蚂蚁！冬天还远着呢！”蚱蜢接着唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>饿的时候，他就摘几片叶子吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是有一天，蚱蜢走出房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吃惊地发现，大地被冰冷的雪覆盖住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！外面很冷。现在要为冬天收集食物了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚱蜢找了又找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是雪覆盖住了草丛，树上也没有叶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚱蜢没有找到任何吃的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他非常冷。于是他回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明天会找到食物的。到那时我会努力工作的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天，我就能找到食物了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他没吃晚餐，直接睡觉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，蚱蜢看到一只蚂蚁经过他的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，一只蚂蚁。说不定他知道草和树叶去哪儿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你好，亲爱的蚂蚁。在哪儿有树叶和草？我很饿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太晚了，蚱蜢。你难道不知道现在已经到冬天了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你应该早点儿储存一些食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在你不能找到任何树叶或草了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我可以的。我可以为冬天做准备。你等着瞧吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，冬天已经来了，现在已经太晚了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚱蜢知道蚂蚁是对的，他为自己的懒惰感到羞愧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚱蜢又冷又饿地躺在家里。他开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是多么愚蠢和懒惰啊。现在，我一点儿食物都没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，愚蠢的蚱蜢开始寻找食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他什么也没找到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他确定自己不会找到任何食物了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到处都找不到食物。树上没有叶子，地上没有草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我这个冬天要挨饿了。”蚱蜢开始大声哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚂蚁们听到了蚱蜢的哭声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很善良，也很可怜蚱蜢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看蚱蜢，如果我们不帮他，他会死的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，我们得和他分享食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是蚂蚁和蚱蜢分享了他们的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那天开始，蚱蜢再也不懒惰了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他成为了森林里最勤劳的昆虫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>